@startuml immutable-case-dhcp-pxe
!theme cyborg

title Case 1 - Existing DHCP with PXE flags

start

:DHCP configured with PXE flags\npointing at furyctl's iPXE server;

:Node powered on -> network-boots;
note right
  DHCP tells it where to
  fetch the iPXE bootloader
end note

:furyctl serves the iPXE config\nbased on the node's MAC address;

:Continue to the shared flow;

stop

@enduml
